snippet.title: Carnival Jackpot
snippet.description: Carnival Jackpot The object of this game is to earn point by creating lines of 3 or more like-colored balls in any direction.

snippet.title: Betty's Beer Bar
snippet.description: Betty's Beer Bar Help Betty serve her funny patrons, earn great tips and work her way up the ladder.

snippet.title: Captain Zambo
snippet.description: Captain Zambo A top secret file from the US Defense has been stolen. Your mission is to recover this important file.

snippet.title: Braap Braap
snippet.description: Braap Braap Motocross game with excellent graphics. Try to get on the podium, perform tricks for extra points.

snippet.title: Dragon Fist 3: Age of the Warrior
snippet.description: Dragon Fist 3: Age of the Warrior Excellent 1 vs 1 side view beat em up, based on Chinese martial arts cinema.

snippet.title: Kilroy: Chernobyl Farms
snippet.description: Kilroy: Chernobyl Farms 3D first person shooter with excellent graphics. Kill all the murderous mutants.

snippet.title: Governor of Poker
snippet.description: Governor of Poker Excellent poker game with very sophisticated realistic opponents and beautiful rendered graphics.

snippet.title: GemCraft
snippet.description: GemCraft Excellent Tower Defense game. Use gems to put an end to the threatening waves of corruption.

snippet.title: Anaksha: Female Assassin
snippet.description: Anaksha: Female Assassin Extremely violent sniper shooting game with an excellent story line.

snippet.title: Madness Regent
snippet.description: Madness Regent Side scrolling platform action shooter with excellent graphics. Destroy everything in your way.
